ope, I come\nto you. It rests with you to resurrect\nme. Will you do s-o?\"\n\"Will I?\" cried the humorist.\nAnd turning on the light, he hopped\nfrom bed with a great, glad cry, took\npen and paper and a lot of bound pe\nriodicals dated four years back, and at\nlast accounts was still writing away\nbusily.\nVanishing Pomp.\nHow worldly pride kin pass away,\nI's takin* foh my tex\\\nWhat is a Christmas tree one day\nIs kindlin' wood de nex'.\nIF TOII WAXT BETTKR l.AMP Oil.\nAsk your dealer for Cream of Oil or write\nTh\u00ab Van Tilburic Co.. Minneapolis, Minn.\nSome men rob widows and orphans\nand then try to square themselves by\ngiving 10 per cent to the Lord.\nYou never can reach a dignity by\nleaping over a duty.\nGood will to man is the best kind of\ngratitude to God.\nGASTORIA\nFor Infants and Children,\nThe Kind You Have\nAlways Bought\nBears the\nSignature\nPOft 8TIFFNE88,\nSORENESS,\nIn\nUse\nFor Over\nThirty Years\nGASTORIA\nTHE CINTAUN COMPANY, NTW VOMN CLTV.\nW. L. Douglas $4 and $5 Gilt Edge Shoes Cannot Be Equalled At Any Price\n\u2022fCAIITIOW, W. U I) uk aft name and price i\u00a7 atamr^d on bottom. Talc* Wo ftahctltute*\npom by the best d*\u00bbalfrR everywhere. Shoes nuulf i tmm factory to any pArt of the world. IIIoa.\nVated Catalog free to any addrea*. \\V. 1.. lfOlOl.Att, Brockton, Mum.\nE TABU SHED fo\ns v I E S U S W O O\nDi RErCT TciJo a nJD SAVE SMALL DEALER\nESTABLISHED 1879.\nWOODWARD CO.\nMinneapolis GRAIN COMMISSION. Da\nColor\nEyeltU\nbxelutivtly.\nS_\nP,!BERGMAN 6rCO., OT. PAUL,MINN. I\nPROFITS.\niMM'EOmr RETURNil\nRTT- FOR PRICE LIST ANO SHIPPING TAGS. I\n9\nTWO CURES OF ECZEMA\nBaby Had Severe Attack\u2014Grandfather\nSuffered Torments with It\u2014\nOwe Recovery to Cuticura.\n\"In ISS-t my grandson, a babe, had\nan attack of eczema, and after trying\nthe doctors to the extent of heavy bills\nand an increase of the disease and suf-.\nfering, I recommended Cuticura and\nin a few weeks the child was well. He,\nis to-day a strong man 